Appendix: Key Assumptions and Sources

FAA fleet data is extrapolated from CY2023 survey using FAA\'s 0.6%
annual growth projection. Based-aircraft counts for 5C1 (Boerne Stage)
are estimated; the field is privately owned and not consistently
reported in FAA 5010 data. Insurance premiums are industry averages from
Insureon, Hartford, and SmartFinancial---actual quotes will vary by
claims history and specific coverage terms. Dugosh Aviation annual
volume is estimated at 50--100+ based on shop size and market position;
actual numbers should be confirmed during partnership discussions. Texas
franchise tax threshold of \$2,470,000 reflects the 2024 increase;
confirm current threshold at comptroller.texas.gov before filing.
Revenue projections assume no significant competitive entry into the
Hill Country market during the three-year projection window.
